snippet.title: Prepare For Warp Graphical Updates 11/11
snippet.description:
Coming along nicely! New bloom effects, and a new ship shader that can handle things like engine glow and complicated blinkylight patterns. Asteroids also improved.

Available in Early Access on Steam November 18. Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1805960/Prepare_For_Warp_Unlimited_Edition_Beyond_Insanji/

Join the Beta on Google Play Store https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.SmilingCatEntertainment.PrepareForWarpFree

Join me on 11/12 at COGG's monthly Prototype and Play event, from 6pm-9pm Eastern: https://discord.gg/R34SPGAT
